name: Magellan Outdoors Men's Laguna Madre Solid Short Sleeve Fishing Shirt
shortDescription: The Magellan Outdoors Men's Laguna Madre Solid Short Sleeve Fishing Shirt has 2 hook-and-loop pockets and a relaxed fit.
longDescription: Slip on the Magellan Outdoors Men's Laguna Madre Solid Short Sleeve Fishing Shirt and make way for the docks: it's the moment you've been waiting for. Crafted to keep you comfortable from line drop to the big haul in, this fishing shirt features moisture-wicking and UPF technologies to keep you dry, comfortable and protected from the sun's harsh rays. Two pockets store your most important essentials, and this shirt is ventilated to keep you nice and cool after a long day by the water.
